        <h2>Tips for Finding the Perfect Fit</h2>
        <p>Our clothing is designed to fit true to size, but everyone’s body is different. If you’re unsure, here are some tips to help:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Measure Yourself:</strong> Use a tape measure to measure your chest, waist, and hips, and compare those measurements to our size chart.</li>
            <li><strong>Consider the Fabric:</strong> Some fabrics stretch more than others. If you prefer a looser fit, opt for natural fabrics like cotton.</li>
            <li><strong>Check the Fit:</strong> If you’re between sizes, consider whether you prefer a more fitted or relaxed look.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>If you still have questions, feel free to <a href="contact.ejs">contact us</a> for further assistance.</p>
